
WebView: we are building a web app in WebView: https://developer.android.com/guide/webapps/webview

PhoneGap: a software development framework by Adobe System, which is used to develop mobile applications. 
To develop apps using PhoneGap, the developer does not require to have knowledge of mobile programming language 
but only web-development languages like, HTML, CSS, and JScript:  https://www.tutorialspoint.com/phonegap/index.htm

Native Apps vs Web Apps vs Hybrid Apps: please read the following article:  https://www.mobiloud.com/blog/native-web-or-hybrid-apps/

